label: HelpMenu
text: Recharge application has two modulesSMS based recharge (Offline)GPRS based recharge (Online)SMS based recharge (Offline)SMS based recharge works by sending SMS from your SIM card to our server number so please make sure that you have configured PIN correctly.Normal messaging charges applies for each request.GPRS based recharge (Online)GPRS based recharge users GPRS connection to communicate with our server so please make sure that you have configured User Id or Username and Password correctly and GPRS connection should activated on your handset/number if you don't know the User Id or Username then please contact your administrator.GPRS/Data charges appliesHandling recharge disputes Help
